 existing Autolabeling Configuration except in the database, which makes it tedious to debug a pipeline.\r\nIt should be pretty easy to include editing these through the Admin UI:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nclass AutoLabelingConfigAdmin(admin.ModelAdmin):                \r\n    list_display = ('project', 'model_name', 'model_attrs',)    \r\n    ordering = ('project',)                                     \r\n                                                                \r\n    def get_readonly_fields(self, request, obj=None):           \r\n        if obj:                                                 \r\n            return [\"model_name\"]                               \r\n        else:                                                   \r\n            return []                                           \r\n                                                                \r\nadmin.site.register(AutoLabelingConfig, AutoLabelingConfigAdmin)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhich would give you:\r\n![doccano-autolabel-admin](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35134759/122774733-c0bf4a80-d2a9-11eb-8bfb-249a2c330850.png)\r\n\r\nIf this is appreciated i would be happy to create a MR :)","closed_by":{"login":"Hironsan","id":6737785,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY3Mzc3ODU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6737785?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan","html_url":"https://github.com/Hironsan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Hironsan/events{/privacy}","received_ev